{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_04_01_short",
  "title": "白石千紗 1話 最高の衣装デザイン (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-02-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.2742073834
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、千紗\nこれからダンスレッスンか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ Chisa.\nHeading to dance practice now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.3910888154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、お姉ちゃんと二人で\n新ユニットの振り付けを練習するんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I'm practicing the choreography with my sister\nfor our new unit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.9189031918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さん、私とお姉ちゃんを\n新ユニットに選んでくれてありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…{user}-san‚ thank you for choosing my sister\nand me for the new unit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.5232542381,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんとユニットを組めるなんて夢みたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's like a dream to be in a unit with my sister.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、沙季と組めるのが本当に嬉しいんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ you're really happy to be paired with Saki.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "はい……だって、お姉ちゃんは私の憧れだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… after all‚ my sister is my idol…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "私が小さい頃、お姉ちゃんがアイドルの真似をして\n歌ってくれたことがあるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I was little‚ she used to imitate idols\nand sing for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.4421081896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "その時のお姉ちゃんは凄くキラキラしていて……\n私もこんな風になりたいって思ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She looked so shiny then…\nI've always wanted to be like her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.6729479581,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}